_sText:
zm Urban Downtown Final

Well guys. This is it. I've been working on this map for a while now. And the job is done.
This is the final version.
It's a nice downtown with a bank, a gas station, a dance club, a movie theater, and a lot more.

Secrets

- Password protected door that leads you to the secret gun and a shortcut to the dance club.
- A secret mini game with a secret end. Hit 200 in the TopHATTwaffle mini game to start the secret end.
- Teleports

Some good places to hide, climb and  make a good cade.

Spawn Points: 64

Thanks to:

d00d: For the fantastic props
P3TR05.99 - For the logic keypad
TopHATTwaffle - For the Daft Punk Prefab
johbal - For the Shawnee Bank
audiOtrash - For parts of the cinema front and the Rocking Music prefab
JasenM - Trap

A special thanks to the guys at ICC server, specialy Sandfly. This project would not be possible, with this quality, without you guys.

The map is a huge bsp. But today most people have ultra fast internet connection so I don't think this will be a problem.
